  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nMemory spiked during archive state\r\n\r\n![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1105347927548907600/1113289049235525652/Screenshot_2023-05-31_at_09.12.07.png)\r\non feat1(tuyen/revert_PR_5520) memory is stable for a while then spiked at 17:46:15, then stable again. The incident is respective to the below log\r\n```\r\nMay-30 17:46:00.198[chain]         ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: Archive states completed finalizedEpoch=204802\r\n```\r\n\r\non beta, rss is not stable but also spiked at 17:33:15, this is respective to the archive state task:\r\n```\r\nMay-30 17:33:11.024[chain]         ^[[36mverbose^[[39m: Archiving of finalized blocks complete totalArchived=32, finalizedEpoch=204800\r\n```\r\n\r\n![](https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1105347927548907600/1113289877396668436/Screenshot_2023-05-31_at_09.15.29.png)\r\n\r\nmore context: https://discord.com/channels/593655374469660673/1105347927548907600/1113289049629798520\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nMemory is stable\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\n_No response_\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating system\n\nLinux\n\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\n\ntuyen/revert_PR_5520",
